@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = ((0.43 * (v0 + 0.89 - v2 + 0.93)) - wp.abs((v1 + 0.75 * tmp + 0.90)))
    v0 = wp.cos(((v0 + 0.56 / v0 + 0.13) / wp.abs(tmp + 0.40)))
    tmp = ((v1 / 0.27) / v1)
    v1 = 0.17
    v2 = wp.exp((v1 / 0.71))
    data[tid] = v0
